author: Star staff
title: Blue Jays news conference with Alex Anthopoulos: Live at 10 a.m.
text:
Blue Jays GM Alex Anthopoulos will host his annual year-end news conference at 10 a.m., three days after Toronto was eliminated from the playoffs by Kansas City.
Questions swirl around Anthopoulos’s future with contract expiring at the end of the month.
